From b3ed9e5611d8eb1b6ad41379dba3a1309f1545ca Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: GIA Refactor <refactor@gia.local>
Date: Thu, 28 May 2026 08:34:54 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] refactor: modular portals architecture

- Add 12 UserRole enum with portal mapping
- AppUser: Set<UserRole>, departmentId, studyGroupId, primaryPortal
- CustomUserDetails: multi-role authorities
- SecurityConfig: /portal/* routing with role checks
- AuthController: returns roles[], availablePortals[], primaryPortal
- 6 portal controllers: gek, deanery, department, admin, methodist, student
- Frontend: authStore with multi-role support
- PortalSelector: post-login portal selection screen
- 6 portal Apps with dedicated sidebars
- Sidebar: grouped by portal sections
